name: Last Flower
description:
There are many wonderful and beautiful things in this world. But what is capable of conveying the glory of this world? Flowers are one of those things; they have always made me stay for a moment and behold their beauty. But even beauties can die.So I would like to keep the moment not only in my memory, but also on this card and share it with the rest of us.

Analog photography & signed in digital
